"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses the `set_xticks` and `set_xticklabels` methods. The `set_xticks` method expects a list of positions (floats or integers) where the ticks should be placed, not the actual date values. Similarly, `set_xticklabels` should be used to set the labels for these positions, not the date values directly.\",\n  \"patch\": \"17c17,18\\n<ax.set_xticks(df.date.unique())\\n---\\n>ax.set_xticks(range(len(df.date.unique())))\\n>ax.set_xticklabels(labels=df.date.dt.strftime('%Y-%m').unique(), rotation=45)\"\n}"